{"tid":234361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實「準」同「准」係咪咁難分點用？","createTime":"2017-05-08T08:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T09:47:29.000Z","uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f823528403a14c8144bbf72fe53e3a275562537","tid":234361,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"fb成堆差不多先生係咪睇得太多殘體字<br />\n忘記咗「準」同「准」點用呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜柒係「唔準搞藝術」呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tvmosthk/photos/a.1625961874318810.1073741828.1625935910988073/1892362677678727/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftvmosthk%2Fphotos%2Fa.1625961874318810.1073741828.1625935910988073%2F1892362677678727%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=59d55661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tvmosthk/photos/a.1625961874318810.1073741828.1625935910988073/1892362677678727/?type=3</a><br />\n有幾唔準確呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔止依個post，琴日一有新聞就成班人留comments，十個有9個都「唔準」「唔準」，你地用字就唔準啦<br />\n<br />\n以前香港人根本唔會錯依啲殘體字混淆嘅字，依家就成街都「制造、電制、唔準、准備」<br />\n我唔撚係正字撚捉你「吾系甘牙」，但都唔係錯支那蝗嘅字呀？<br />\n以前香港人就大大聲笑一睇篇文嘅繁簡錯字就知作者係支那人，依家都知呀，港皮支心嘅支那人囉<br />\n定係陰謀論，啲傳媒故意去請啲人或者叫啲編輯用錯字去染污香港人嘅文化水平，等啲五毛可以大大聲話笑返香港人轉頭再話咩「唔準只係話大陸人，香港人都係！華人DNA！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4efb6998cfabe046f6d12d3013b3a9ba99b5c20","tid":234361,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:06:24.000Z","msg":"準，accurate<br />\n准，allowed"},{"pid":"1b345ca88cc617e64fbe589ddd8d9115f00ac7a7","tid":234361,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準，accurate<br />\n准，allowed</blockquote><br />\n咁&ldquo;準&rdquo;備呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097503360ad0dcdb3495ee3361f9e12ccb4eca1d","tid":234361,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n廿幾年來都係甘用"},{"pid":"994fd46c82600cc91151be2fb2ff42d9a80f9a73","tid":234361,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下<br />\n廿幾年來都係甘用</blockquote><br />\n甘你老母"},{"pid":"a867505ea081d28f944963274690d9fc30ff99e8","tid":234361,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"準: 準備 準確<br />\n准:準許"},{"pid":"9d7b4faa09fdb73f605909ab1775a78d9bfe8f31","tid":234361,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下<br />\n廿幾年來都係甘用</blockquote><br />\n甘你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766d4b0d768223d680aa6b5ac1e8f8fa4485c1d0","tid":234361,"uid":72169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:23:23.000Z","msg":"制掣製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e7b59a34b073a98e644f00750186843eb71fc3","tid":234361,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"佢鑒字都打錯成鋻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bf684ed011bc04985a8b7df23e66727f964751","tid":234361,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下<br />\n廿幾年來都